Reasoning: The paper discusses fair scheduling algorithms for allocating resources in distributed application frameworks, specifically focusing on Spark workloads on Mesos. This falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC) and could also be considered under the sub-categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), systems and control (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and programming languages (cs.PL).
